  "description": "mdk - project health detail (insight-fed). Drill-down companion to mdk-daily-insights: per-project health_score history, cost/latency/quality trend sparklines from the insights trends{} block, and the failure-cluster breakdown from top_failures[]. Reads from the ADR 047 Observability Intelligence API (GET /api/v1/observability/insights) via a JSON/Infinity datasource, with one raw-metric reference panel (mdk.run.cost_usd, mdk.job.duration_ms) from Prometheus for ground-truth comparison. See dashboards/grafana/insights/README.md. NOTE: ADR 047 endpoints are not on main yet - the insight panels render their documented-gap state until then.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "links": [
    {"title": "Daily insights (fleet)", "type": "link", "url": "/d/mdk-daily-insights", "targetBlank": true, "icon": "external link"},
    {"title": "Raw-metric golden signals (#518)", "type": "link", "url": "/d/mdk-golden-signals", "targetBlank": true, "icon": "external link"}
  ],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": 401,
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "title": "How to read this dashboard (project health)",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## mdk - project health detail\n\n**What this shows.** Everything about **one project's** health over time: the composite `health_score` trend, the cost/latency/quality `trends{}` sparklines, and the `top_failures[]` cluster breakdown - all from the ADR 047 Observability Intelligence API. Pick the project with `$project` (top-left).\n\n**Normal.** `health_score` flat near 100; trend sparklines flat or gently improving; failure-cluster table short.\n\n**If you see X.** A dip in the score lines up (via the red anomaly annotations) with the trend that regressed - jump there, then into the failure clusters, then out to Jaeger / the NL-query UI.\n\n> **Gap banner (ADR 047 not on main yet).** The score-history, trends, and failure-cluster panels read `GET /api/v1/observability/insights`, delivered by **ADR 047**, which is **not on `main`** at the time this pack shipped. Those panels show empty/placeholder data until the endpoint is deployed - expected, not a misconfiguration. The single raw-metric comparison panel (Prometheus) works standalone today. Wire the datasource per `dashboards/grafana/insights/README.md`.\n\n**Cross-surface.** Fleet view: `dashboards/grafana/insights/mdk-daily-insights.json`. Raw metrics: `dashboards/grafana/mdk-golden-signals.json` (#518)."
      }
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 4},
      "id": 410,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Health-score history (0-100; green >= 80, amber 50-79, red < 50)",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "id": 411,
      "datasource": {"type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource", "uid": "${DS_INSIGHTS}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 5},
      "title": "health_score over time",
      "description": "Time series of the 0-100 composite health_score for $project, from GET /api/v1/observability/insights (history[].health_score keyed by ts). Threshold bands: red < 50, amber 50-79, green >= 80. Red anomaly annotations overlay the dips. Empty until ADR 047 ships.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "gradientMode": "scheme",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "dashed"}
          },
          "max": 100,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "red", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 50},
              {"color": "green", "value": 80}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "none"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull", "min", "mean"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource", "uid": "${DS_INSIGHTS}"},
          "refId": "A",
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "/api/v1/observability/insights",
          "root_selector": "history",
          "filters": [
            {"field": "project", "operator": "regex", "value": "$project"},
            {"field": "environment", "operator": "regex", "value": "$environment"}
          ],
          "columns": [
            {"selector": "ts", "text": "time", "type": "timestamp_epoch_s"},
            {"selector": "health_score", "text": "health_score", "type": "number"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 13},
      "id": 420,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Trends (cost / latency / quality sparklines, from insights trends{})",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "id": 421,
      "datasource": {"type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource", "uid": "${DS_INSIGHTS}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 14},
      "title": "Cost trend",
      "description": "trends.cost sparkline + last value for $project, from GET /api/v1/observability/insights. The percent delta-vs-baseline drives the up/down coloring (cost rising = red). Empty until ADR 047 ships.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "custom": {"drawStyle": "line"},
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "yellow", "value": 10}, {"color": "red", "value": 25}]},
          "unit": "percent"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "/^delta_pct$/", "values": false},
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "targets": [
