      "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 14},
      "title": "Latency trend (p95)",
      "description": "trends.latency_p95 sparkline + delta-vs-baseline for $project, from GET /api/v1/observability/insights. Rising p95 = red. Empty until ADR 047 ships.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "custom": {"drawStyle": "line"},
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "yellow", "value": 10}, {"color": "red", "value": 25}]},
          "unit": "percent"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "/^delta_pct$/", "values": false},
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource", "uid": "${DS_INSIGHTS}"},
          "refId": "A",
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "/api/v1/observability/insights",
          "root_selector": "trends.latency_p95",
          "filters": [{"field": "project", "operator": "regex", "value": "$project"}],
          "columns": [
            {"selector": "ts", "text": "time", "type": "timestamp_epoch_s"},
            {"selector": "value", "text": "value", "type": "number"},
            {"selector": "delta_pct", "text": "delta_pct", "type": "number"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "id": 423,
      "datasource": {"type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource", "uid": "${DS_INSIGHTS}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 14},
      "title": "Quality trend (eval pass-rate)",
      "description": "trends.quality (eval pass-rate %) sparkline + delta for $project, from GET /api/v1/observability/insights. Falling quality = red (note: lower is worse here, so thresholds are inverted vs cost/latency). Empty until ADR 047 ships.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "custom": {"drawStyle": "line"},
          "mappings": [],
          "max": 100,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "red", "value": null}, {"color": "yellow", "value": 80}, {"color": "green", "value": 95}]},
          "unit": "percent"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "/^value$/", "values": false},
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource", "uid": "${DS_INSIGHTS}"},
          "refId": "A",
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "/api/v1/observability/insights",
          "root_selector": "trends.quality",
          "filters": [{"field": "project", "operator": "regex", "value": "$project"}],
          "columns": [
            {"selector": "ts", "text": "time", "type": "timestamp_epoch_s"},
            {"selector": "value", "text": "value", "type": "number"},
            {"selector": "delta_pct", "text": "delta_pct", "type": "number"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": 424,
      "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 21},
      "title": "Sub-panel: how to read the trends",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**What.** Three sparklines from the insights `trends{}` block (`cost`, `latency_p95`, `quality`), each showing the recent series plus a **delta-vs-baseline %**.\n\n**Normal.** Cost & latency deltas near 0%; quality >= 95%.\n\n**If you see X.**\n\n- **Cost** delta > 25% (red) -> token regression; cross-check the raw `mdk.run.cost_usd` panel below and run `mdk eval` for the project's agents.\n- **Latency p95** delta > 25% (red) -> correlate with the deploy annotation on the score-history chart; open Jaeger from the #518 golden-signals dashboard.\n- **Quality** < 80% (red; inverted thresholds - lower is worse) -> eval drift; open the NL-query UI / the agent's regression set.\n\n_Color thresholds documented in `dashboards/grafana/insights/README.md`._"
      }
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 24},
      "id": 430,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Failure clusters (from insights top_failures[])",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "id": 431,
      "datasource": {"type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource", "uid": "${DS_INSIGHTS}"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 25},
      "title": "Failure-cluster breakdown",
      "description": "top_failures[] for $project from GET /api/v1/observability/insights: clustered error signatures with count, share of failures, a representative trace_id and run_id, and the cluster's first/last-seen. Links drill to Jaeger + the NL-query UI. Empty until ADR 047 ships.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"custom": {"align": "auto", "filterable": true}, "mappings": []},
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "share"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "unit", "value": "percentunit"},
              {"id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": {"type": "gauge", "mode": "gradient"}},
              {"id": "max", "value": 1},
              {"id": "min", "value": 0}
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "trace"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "links", "value": [{"title": "Open Jaeger trace", "url": "http://localhost:16686/trace/${__data.fields.trace_id}", "targetBlank": true}]}
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "ask"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "links", "value": [{"title": "Ask in the NL-query UI", "url": "/a/mdk-nl-query?project=${__data.fields.project}&q=show%20failures%20like%20${__data.fields.signature}", "targetBlank": true}]}
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {"showHeader": true, "sortBy": [{"displayName": "count", "desc": true}]},
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource", "uid": "${DS_INSIGHTS}"},
          "refId": "A",
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "/api/v1/observability/insights",
          "root_selector": "top_failures",
          "filters": [{"field": "project", "operator": "regex", "value": "$project"}],
          "columns": [
            {"selector": "signature", "text": "signature", "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "count", "text": "count", "type": "number"},
            {"selector": "share", "text": "share", "type": "number"},
            {"selector": "first_seen", "text": "first_seen", "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "last_seen", "text": "last_seen", "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "trace_id", "text": "trace", "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "run_id", "text": "ask", "type": "string"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 34},
      "id": 440,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Ground-truth check (raw metrics, #518 catalog)",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"},
      "description": "Raw-metric ground truth for the trends above: per-tenant cost rate (mdk.run.cost_usd) and job latency p95 (mdk.job.duration_ms) from Prometheus. Use this to sanity-check that an insights trend matches the underlying metric. Same instruments + 30s SLO line as the #518 golden-signals dashboard.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "lineWidth": 2, "showPoints": "never", "thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "line"}},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "red", "value": 30000}]},
          "unit": "ms"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "cost (USD/hr)"},
            "properties": [{"id": "unit", "value": "currencyUSD"}, {"id": "custom.axisPlacement", "value": "right"}]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 35},
      "id": 441,
      "links": [
        {"title": "Open #518 golden signals", "url": "/d/mdk-golden-signals", "targetBlank": true}
      ],
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "targets": [
        {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "editorMode": "code", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(mdk_job_duration_ms_milliseconds_bucket[$__rate_interval])))", "legendFormat": "latency p95 (ms)", "range": true, "refId": "A"},
        {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "editorMode": "code", "expr": "sum by (tenant) (rate(mdk_run_cost_usd_total{tenant=~\"$tenant\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 3600", "legendFormat": "cost (USD/hr)", "range": true, "refId": "B"}
      ],
      "title": "Raw latency p95 + cost rate (ground truth for the trends)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": 442,
      "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 43},
      "title": "Sub-panel: ground-truth check",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**What.** The same instruments the insights `trends{}` are derived from, rendered raw from Prometheus (`mdk.job.duration_ms` p95, `mdk.run.cost_usd` rate). This is the **trust-but-verify** panel: if a trend sparkline disagrees with the raw metric, suspect the insights pipeline (stale `observability_insights` rollup) before chasing the agent.\n\n**Normal.** Raw lines track the trend sparklines above.\n\n**If you see X.** Trend says \"cost +40%\" but the raw cost rate is flat -> the insights rollup is stale or mis-scoped; check the ADR 047 job. Raw spike with no trend/anomaly -> the anomaly detector missed it; widen the lookback or lower the sensitivity (ADR 047 config)."
      }
    }
  ],
